Class ServletWebServerSettings

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.boot.web.server.servlet.ServletWebServerSettings
public class ServletWebServerSettings extends Object
Settings for a servlet WebServer to be created by a ConfigurableServletWebServerFactory.
Since:
4.0.0
Author:
Andy Wilkinson
